{"tid":344039,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想拍條mv做生日禮物，求見議","createTime":"2017-08-02T03:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T04:00:04.000Z","uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59a28f9f3f9c436195335ad757bdc912008217f4","tid":344039,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"嚟緊朋友嘅女朋友生日，<br />\n想拍個mv做生日禮物<br />\n<br />\n歌會用陪著你走<br />\n得番大半個月都唔知點拍好<br />\n<br />\n因為我朋友冇朋友的，所以只可以拍一兩個人嘅mv，冇乜演員<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有冇咩suggest可以點拍啊？<br />\n<br />\n多數會用幾多個景㗎？<br />\n4個會唔會太少呢？<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇剪片軟件可以推介下？<br />\n<br />\n我同我朋友都係新手，希望大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb3be08de0533e708d40adb6bc266badb2a10f3","tid":344039,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:30:19.000Z","msg":"樓主rap咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己一個拍都得啦，拍多幾個鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：之前幫過fd整，效果出黎柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd192ca078694e1a3a41e28f27bc4dd39cb518b5","tid":344039,"uid":40460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"超低成本同技術制作：<br />\n用你哋啲相同上網搵嘅圖片做powerpoint slide<br />\n加入音樂<br />\n再用software 錄低/save as 影片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就用手機app"},{"pid":"e3dbea589adbf6d14051b92bd43d18c583cbbf59","tid":344039,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主嘅外型係咩類型？"},{"pid":"4934a50c0a9928940846f2281ade2a1534d1b84a","tid":344039,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主rap咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己一個拍都得啦，拍多幾個鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：之前幫過fd整，效果出黎柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算柒，收到果個都應該都好開心<br />\n但我依家完全冇概念應該點拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebcb47c863aea1d9852bd40ef07ecd5513f39a9","tid":344039,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下樓主嘅外型係咩類型？</blockquote><br />\n比人感覺比較年輕，但成三張野了<br />\n<br />\n正常招牌掉落嚟死10個果啲"},{"pid":"1dcd29534f314bad267c5997587858c5e63b13f3","tid":344039,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超低成本同技術制作：<br />\n用你哋啲相同上網搵嘅圖片做powerpoint slide<br />\n加入音樂<br />\n再用software 錄低/save as 影片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就用手機app</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個之前試過了，都成十年前<br />\n但同一個人，今次想試下識郁嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實係咁啱之前睇番余文樂扮女裝個mv先有呢個想法<br />\n<br />\n十年真係乜都送過曬，生日禮物真係好令人煩惱"},{"pid":"75de0b6136358bc3a8bfd7d3337526e5aebac355","tid":344039,"uid":122858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"朋友個女朋友出唔出鏡?<br />\n<br />\n出鏡:唔驚喜<br />\n<br />\n唔出鏡: &quot;陪著你走~~~&quot; 朋友拖著第二條女??<br />\n<br />\n做左STORY BOARD先，知自己要拍D咩，唔好以為埋到牙先拍就OK，導演一定要知自己要咩，AFTER EFFECT剪片幾好用，"},{"pid":"0172c512d4c5bcf3a858c086b96bbbafef916c62","tid":344039,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"其實有咁7得咁7就最好<br />\n當然要7得黎搞笑"},{"pid":"648087b125917700db7222a621dacdcc8795720a","tid":344039,"uid":40460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>超低成本同技術制作：<br />\n用你哋啲相同上網搵嘅圖片做powerpoint slide<br />\n加入音樂<br />\n再用software 錄低/save as 影片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就用手機app</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個之前試過了，都成十年前<br />\n但同一個人，今次想試下識郁嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實係咁啱之前睇番余文樂扮女裝個mv先有呢個想法<br />\n<br />\n十年真係乜都送過曬，生日禮物真係好令人煩惱</blockquote><br />\n咁你啲朋友要好入戲先得<br />\n太正經出到嚟個效果會好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd76895fb0e680e6c86ab7c46811eaa0ca0